# Intuit Design System - Elevation Token Library

## Primitive Elevation Tokens (DO NOT USE DIRECTLY IN PLUGINS)

- `--elevation-0`: 0 0 0 0
- `--elevation-1`: 0 1px 4px 0
- `--elevation-2`: 0 2px 8px 0
- `--elevation-3`: 0 4px 16px 0
- `--elevation-4`: 0 6px 24px 0

## Semantic Elevation Tokens (USE THESE IN PLUGINS)

### Level0
- `--elevation-level-0`: --elevation-0 /* elevation.level.4 elevation.4 Modal dialog */

### Level1
- `--elevation-level-1`: --elevation-1 /* Internal component parts (slider handle, switch handle) */

### Level2
- `--elevation-level-2`: --elevation-2 /* Menu, tooltip, toast */

### Level3
- `--elevation-level-3`: --elevation-3 /* Drawer */

### Level4
- `--elevation-level-4`: --elevation-4 /* Modal dialog */
